superEvent.name: Back to Netball
superEvent.description:
Running across England since 2010, over 100,000 women have taken part in Back to Netball and realised the benefits of getting involved. From losing weight, developing the body’s cardiovascular system and improving muscle tone, taking part in Back to Netball is great for you in so many ways.

Run by passionate and enthusiastic coaches, sessions usually cover the basics of the game including passing, footwork and shooting, finishing with a friendly game to put the skills you've learnt into practice.

You don’t need any special kit, just clothes that you feel comfortable exercising in and trainers. Make sure you bring some water too!
